Open Meditation

	Philosophy

		-
			Open Meditation is to enter a mental state where is open to any idea, no matter how
			absurd or offensive they would otherwise regard it.
		-

	Principles

		Abnormality Trigger

			-
				An abnormality trigger is a stimulus that triggers abnormal phenomena in the mind
				or body of a subject, and can either be intentionally generated or unintentionally
				received.
